<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَسَكَنْتَ لَحْدًا قَدْ يَضِيقُ لِضَيْقِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>صَدْرَ الْحَلِيمِ وَصَابِرُ الْحَيَوَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَسَمِعْتَ قَرْعَ نِعَالِهِمْ مِنْ بَعْدِ مَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَضَعُوكَ فِي الْبَيْتِ الصَّغِيرِ الثَّانِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِيهِ الظَّلامُ كَذَا السُّكُونُ مُخَيَّمٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَالرُّوحُ رَدَّ وَجَاءَكَ الْمَلَكَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَهُنَا الْحَقِيقَةُ وَالْمُحَقِّقُ قَدْ أَتَى<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هَذَا مَقَامُ النَّصْرِ وَالْخُذْلانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِنْ كُنْتَ فِي الدُّنْيَا لِرَبِّكَ مُخْلِصًا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَدْعُوهُ بِالتَّوْحِيدِ وَالإِيمَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَتَظَلُّ تَرْفُلُ فِي النَّعِيمِ مُرَفَهًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِفَسِيحِ قَبْرٍ طَاهِرِ الأَرْكَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَلَكَ الرَّفِيقُ عَنِ الْفِرَاقَ مُسَلِّيًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>يُغْنِي عَنِ الأَحْبَابِ وَالأَخْدَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فُتِحَتْ عَلَيْكَ مِنَ الْجِنَانِ نَوَافِذٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَأْتِيكَ بِالأَنْوَارِ وَالرَّيْحَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَتَظَلُّ مُنْشَرِحَ الْفُؤَادِ مُنْعَمًا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>حَتَّى يَقُومَ إِلَى الْقَضَا الثَّقَلانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>تَأْتِي الْحِسَابَ وَقَدْ فَتَحَتَ صَحِيفَةً<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِالنُّورِ قَدْ كُتِبَتْ وَبِالرِّضْوَانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَتَرَى الْخَلائِقَ خَائِفِينَ لِذَنْبِهِمْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَتَسِيرُ أَنْتَ بِعِزَّةٍ وَأَمَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>